<div class="contact-wrapper">

    <div class="contact-card">

        <div class="contact-header">
            <h1>Contact IncentIQ Support</h1>
            <p>We're here to help with IncentIQ configuration, quotas, plans, payouts, and technical support.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="contact-content">

            <div class="contact-section">
                <h2>Need Assistance?</h2>

                <p>
                    The IncentIQ Support Team is available to assist with application setup,
                    compensation plans, quota management, sales transactions, incentive calculations,
                    reporting, troubleshooting, and general platform inquiries.
                </p>

                <div class="support-note">
                    For the fastest resolution, please include relevant details such as user name,
                    plan name, quota period, error message, or screenshots when contacting support.
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="contact-grid">

                <div class="contact-box">
                    <h3>Email Support</h3>
                    <p>
                        <a href="mailto:Contact@CtrlAltNow.com">
                            Contact@CtrlAltNow.com
                        </a>
                    </p>
                    <p>For technical issues, questions, and support requests.</p>
